      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ONE MARGARITA (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (17.33) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Form here sound including five wins. Has won three of five starts from this draw. Better than last start and worth following up. SECRET SUPER (1) made light work of the tricky draw with a fast early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing third (16.84) at Murray Bridge over 300m. Has good speed and is aided by the cherry draw. Hard to beat again. AGENT TWENTY ONE (5) looks close to another win after finishing third last time (20.21) at Angle Park. Form here at this distance is sound. Has the ability and rates a key chance this line-up. BOOKALOO (7) deserves plenty of thought at her first run at this circuit.",
